<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10101565>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–7. 1) Hylaeogena speculum, front; 2) Hedwigiella jureceki, front; 3) Euhylaeogena byattae, front; 4) H. jureceki, male aedeagus; 5) Hedwigiella cbellamyi, male aedeagi; 6) E. byattae, male aedeagi; 7) Euhylaeogena clbellamyi, male aedeagi. Scale bars in Figs. 1–3 = 0.5 mm; in Figs. 4–7 = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10101565/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10101569>
    dc:description "Figs. 8–11. Habitus, dorsal views. 8) Hylaeogena bellamyi, holotype; 9) Hedwigiella cbellamyi, holotype; 10) Euhylaeogena byattae, male, INBIOCRI002275660; 11) Euhylaeogena clbellamyi, holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10101569/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

